      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox paired with a speed-sensitive variable M differential lock. The chassis integrity is superlative, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service using VAC coated bearings. Performance is bolstered by a refreshed cooling system and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining factory-spec kinematics. The exterior retains its original luster with consistent paint-meter readings across all panels. A mechanically flawless specimen for the serious collector seeking peak longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
      "price": 44500.0,
